      "body": "Useful framing for this ticket: the root router is where the separation becomes legible.\n\nIt should tell an agent where truth lives, not duplicate that truth:\n\n- knowledge = what is true and reusable\n- memory = what should be carried forward\n- plan = what we are actively doing\n- generated context = a projection, not the canonical store\n\nSo `CLAUDE.md` / `SKOGAI.md` should stay thin, opinionated, and routing-oriented. Once it turns into an overview dump, it will drift and undermine the separation.",
